description: ----------FAQ---------- Q：MP3 player cannot be connected with bluetooth headset/speaker. 1. First confirm whether there are other players and Bluetooth headphones/speakers around. (eg your phone) you need to erase these devices in bluetooth and turn off the bluetooth switch. Enter the Bluetooth function of the phone, set all the devices under 'MY DEVICES' to 'Forget This Device'. Then turn off the bluetooth function of the phone . 2. Reset your bluetooth headset/speaker, then put it next to MP3 to search and connect. Q：MP3 player Bluetooth searches for the device, but cannot connect successfully. 1.Enter the Bluetooth function-Select the 'Paired Device'-select your Bluetooth device and press the circular button in the middle to select 'Unpair'. 2.Turn off the MP3's Bluetooth, wait a few seconds, and then turn it on again. 3.Put your bluetooth earphone/speaker next to the MP3 player and search on the MP3 again. Multiple searches are possible. (Note: If it still can't be fixed, we can do a firmware update for you.) Ideal for online class, homeschool and assessments, these computer audio & video accessories are classroom must haves for teachers who are looking for durable, rugged headphones that lasts. The B1 Headset comes in Black, Blue, Teal, Red and Bright Red. 3.5 MM HEADSET - Compatible with almost all devices that have 3.5 mm audio jack like laptop, computer, tablets and headset for pc. With a 4 foot long chew proof cord, this durable headset with volume control offers room to move freely preventing any accidental pull-outs. ADDITIONAL FEATURES - Optimized full frequency response of 20 - 20000 Hz delivers an ideal, high-quality sound while an enhanced impedance level of 32 ohms protects against "blow outs" caused by amplification. All of this plus a unidirectional boom microphone that features 100 - 12000 Hz frequency response ensures a crisp and clear 2-way communication best for teacher-student instruction, voice recording and language learning sessions. DROP TESTED AND DURABLE - Gumdrop wired over ear headphones are rigorously drop-tested for falls of up to 6 feet, so they stay in one piece in even the youngest hands. PLUG-AND-PLAY - No need for additional software or Bluetooth connectivity. Easy to use. Simply plug and play!

title: Calibrite ColorChecker Display Plus (CCDIS3PL)
description: Calibrite Photo and Video Calibrite provides colour management solutions to ensure accurate and consistent colour results from capture to print, no matter your colour needs. Calibrite is dedicated to providing the very best solutions for photographers, filmmakers, designers and content creators who love colour and demand the very best tools for their colour-critical workflow. Get predictable results from cameras under any lighting condition and achieve the perfect monitor-to-print match, saving time, ink, and paper. Calibrite ColorChecker Display Plus Professional display calibration for photographers and filmmakers Built with advanced technology to meet the needs of filmmakers, editors, colourists and photographers working with today’s professional monitors, the ColorChecker Display Plus colourimeter ensures the highest level of on-screen colour. Accurately measure luminance/brightness levels up to 2000 nits. Obtain correct neutral detail levels and higher accuracy in dark colours with black current subtraction technology. BT.1886 default gamma curve - beneficial for 3D LUT workflows and HDR supported displays to minimise clipping in dark area, get better behaviour in blacks and smoother detail levels. USB-C compatible with included USB-C to USB-A adapter.       Monitor Calibration Edit and view your footage accurately; ColorChecker Display Plus uses advanced technologies to perfect your colour throughout your production and post-production workflow. Projector Calibration Build an accurate projector profile that considers projected colours, screen colour and room lighting, so that your projected images are showing the way you intended. Software for HDR and video The included ccProfiler software supports HDR and video workflows, as the calibrator has been designed for current and future high-luminance monitors, making it the most capable and future-proof solution available today. Calibrite ColorChecker Display Calibrite ColorChecker Display Pro Calibrite ColorChecker Display Plus Calibrite ColorChecker Display Studio Support for Industry Standard Display Technologies ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ Support for Super-Bright HD and HDR Monitors ✓ Ambient Light Measurement ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ Ambient Light Monitoring ✓ ✓ Projector Profiling ✓ ✓ ✓ ✓ Printer Profiling ✓ Illuminant Measurement 1000 nits 1000 nits 2000 nits 1000 nits Measurement Speed Standard 5X Standard 5X Standard Standard Tripod Mount ✓ ✓ ✓ USB Compatibility USB-A USB-A USB-A and USB-C USB-A

The watchfaces in the watch face store will be updated from time to time, and more surprises are waiting for you to discover!DIY Yourself: In addition, our smartwatch also supports custom watch faces, you can upload your favorite pictures as your watch faces, such as your family, pets, idols, etc. Smartwatch dials to suit different people's aesthetics!   YOUR PERSONAL SMART ASSISTANT As your personal smart assistant, smartwatch has a variety of useful functions. Drink Reminder & Sedentary Reminder: When you are immersed in work and remain sitting for a long time, smart watch will vibrate to remind you to have a rest for a while. The fitness watch can remind you drinking water every once in a while according to your setting to help you keep your body in good state.Raise to Wake: At the set time, watch screen will light up when you raise your hand. You can customize the opening time to avoid bedtime, so as not to disturb your sleep.Weather Forecast: Smart watch will show the weather for the next 7 days, allowing you to check the specific weather at any time without a phone. The weather function needs to be connected to the mobile phone to update in real time.Shake for Photograph: Open the "FitCloudPro" App > Device > Shake for Photograph > Allow access to camera > Shak your smart watch to record beautiful moments.Health Monitoring: The fitness watch records daily steps, distance, calorie consumption. It can track and analyse Sleep time and heart rate, also monitor blood oxygen and blood pressure. All data can be synchronized to your phone for analysis and to help you create a scheduled routine to meet your health goals.Bluetooth Music Control: After connecting the mobile phone Bluetooth, click to control the previous song, next song, play, pause and other operations of the phone without taking your phone out of your pocket.Stopwatch: You can use the stopwatch tool to time your run.Find Phone: When you forget where your phone is, tap the "Find Phone" function on smart watch, your phone will ring and vibrate.Brightness Adjustment: 5 levels Brightness options allow you to easily read in the sun or in the dark.Alarm Clock: You can set a silent vibration alert on the "FitCloudPro" app to wake you up without disturbing your family.Long Battery Life: The smartwatch with 230mAH battery capacity can be fully charged in about 2 hours, and it can be used for up to 2-7 days (Note: depends on individual usage) Comes with a magnetic charging cable. More Practical functions are waiting for you to explore!   ALL-ROUND HEALTH MONITORING Sleep Monitor: Wear the watch to sleep, the sleep tracker will automatically monitor sleep status from 9 PM to 9 AM and provide comprehensive sleep quality analysis (deep sleep, light sleep and wake up). The data will be recorded on the APP, and you can understand your sleep quality through the data and adjust your daily routine.24/7 Heart Rate Monitor: Heart rate watch can monitor heart rate automatically all day. Turn on the “Automatic Health Monitor” in the APP, and the bracelet will automatically measure at set intervals.Boold Oxygen Monitor: Used the newest photoelectric sensing technology, optical measurement is carried out based on the principle, the amount of light absorbed by arterial blood varies with arterial pulsation. Sport watch monitor your blood oxygen saturation when you are unwell or during high-intensity exercise to understand your physical condition at once, helping you have a healthier lifestyle.Blood Pressure Monitor: Best smart watches for women men has a blood pressure monitoring function, and the monitoring data will be recorded on the APP.Women's Health: Womens watch will display different status reminders for different periods such as safe period, menstruation, ovulation and pregnancy. Support data synchronization with Apple Health and Google Fit. Read and Write permissions can be enabled.   YOUR TRAINING COACH IP67 Waterproof: 1 meter deep, 30 minutes. The water resistant design is perfect for sports enthusiasts. You can wear this womens watch whether it's for daily hand washing or rainy days. Note: please don't use in diving, hot water, or environment with corrosive liquids and hot steam. description: Product Description Pelican Protector Cases are made with Copolymer Polypropylene, using an open cell core and solid wall construction, which is stronger and lighter that the completion. You can tell its a Pelican case by the distinctive "twin-ribbed" top surface. Stainless steel pins are used for hinges and handles. The new Double-Throw latches are much easier to open. From the Manufacturer Product DescriptionFrom the ManufacturerANATOMY OF A PELICAN CASEUltimate Equipment ProtectionFor over 30 years Pelican has built a reputation for manufacturing the toughest cases in the world. As a matter of fact, we invented the category. Over these years we've seen our cases used for some fairly crazy activities...and important ones too.Pelican Cases have been thrown out of helicopters in Iraq, floated through frigid fjords in Norway and rolled over by SUVs in Tanzania. With only a few scratches to show on the outside, contents inside are left unscathed. These are minor details for major bragging rights. And that is really what it's all about. Getting your gear from point A to point B in the condition it's meant to be in: intact and functional. Because it might contain a large format camera that will shoot next month's magazine cover or a heart defibrillator that could save a person's life, you can't put a price on it. Stronger by Design Pelican Cases are made with a proprietary combination of homo co-polymers, using an open cell core and solid wall construction, which is stronger and lighter than a solid core wall. Stainless steel pins are used in hinges and handles. WatertightThe secret is the tongue and groove fit with a polymer o-ring acting as a waterproof seal.Cool Under PressureAutomatic Pressure Equalization Valve releases built-up air pressure while keeping water molecules out, resulting in a watertight case that is even easier to open.Easy RollerStainless steel ball bearing wheels last longer and ride smoother. The nylon hub adjacent to the stainless steel is made to resist heat. The result is less wear and tear on the polyurethane wheel. Double-Throw LatchesStainless steel hasp protectors are a Pelican exclusive. The Double-Throw latches are smarter and easier to open: it's the classic "C" clamp design with a secondary movement that works like a pry bar to start the release and offers plenty of leverage to open with a light pull.NameplateCustom engraved nameplates are available for a nominal fee.Reinforced Padlock ProtectorsStainless steel reinforced padlock protectors provide added strength and extra security against cutting and theft.

title: Belkin Soundform Nano - Bluetooth Earbuds for Kids with Built in Microphone - Kids Bluetooth Wireless Earbuds - Bluetooth Earbuds for iPhone, iPad, Galaxy & More - White
description: Belkin SoundForm Nano Wireless Earbuds are the perfect kids Bluetooth headphones. Our Bluetooth earbuds are designed to accompany your kids in virtual classes, while watching educational videos, or on a long ride so they can listen comfortably to music. The SoundForm Nano Earbuds offer fun color options that children will love. The soft silicone ear tips are designed to fit young ears and come in 5 sizes including XXS. Unlike adult Bluetooth headphones and wireless earbuds, SoundForm Nano Earbuds are small and light, providing superior wearing comfort without sacrificing audio quality. Get a full, 24-hour long charge for the case and earbuds from just 2 hours with the included micro-USB charging cable. Kids can get back to listening quickly, just 10 minutes of charge provides one hour of playtime. Kids won't need any help setting up or using their Bluetooth earbuds thanks to simple wire and button-free touch controls for play/pause, volume control, and Bluetooth pairing. And parents can rest easy knowing SoundForm Nano has a volume cap of 85dB to keep volume levels in a safe range. Belkin SoundForm Nano kids earbuds deliver crystal clear audio for unhindered communication. With a built-in microphone, kids will enjoy crisp and clear voice quality, so the conversation flows freely and uninterrupted whether used at school, home, or while traveling, streaming, or gaming! PACKAGE INCLUDES SOUNDFORM Nano Wireless Earbuds for Kids  Charging case  Micro-USB charging cable  5 pairs silicone ear tips   Quick Start Guide

title: Sound BlasterX Katana Multi-Channel Surround Gaming and Entertainment Soundbar - Hardware Processing, Supports Dolby Digital 5.1 Decoding, Bluetooth-Enabled, for PC, Mac, PS4, and Other Consoles
item_weight: 17.64 lbs 5.90 lbs 9.59 lbs 3.97 lbs 5.05 lbs 7.27 lbs
description: Sound BlasterX Katana The Sound BlasterX Katana is as much of a deadly weapon as its namesake. It fits right under your monitor with a slimness that's unmatched by other gaming “sound bars”, and is powered by the award winning multi-core audio DSP making it the world's first true Under Monitor Audio System (UMAS). The Katana gives you an immersive audio experience for your games and movies with the BlasterX Acoustic Engine and Dolby Digital 5.1 Decoder. This audio system embodies the perfect combination of our most powerful 24-bit high resolution DAC and sophisticated 5-driver system. Equipped with a plethora of connectivity options, you can trust the Katana to be one of the most versatile and most powerful speakers to ever grace your desktop. SO SLEEK, YET SO POWERFUL The Katana can be effortlessly tucked right under your monitors and TV. With a slim profile shorter than 60mm, this Under Monitor Audio System is drastically superior in form and function to ordinary “gaming soundbars” and is perfect for all setups. LIGHT UP YOUR SETUP The Katana incorporates the Aurora Reactive lighting system, where its base is lined with 49 programmable LED lights from edge to edge. With the accompanying free Sound Blaster Connect software, you can choose from up to 16.8 million colours and fully customize your ambience lighting effects to create your own unique profile that elevates your visual experiences POWERFUL AUDIO, FLEXIBLE CONNECTIVITY The Katana houses a 5-driver design - two up-firing midbass drivers and two high-excursion tweeters in the soundbar, and one long-throw driver in its subwoofer. Each driver is individually chambered and powered by a DSP-controlled amplifier to deliver ultra-precise audio. In a league of its own, the Katana is enhanced by our proprietary multi-core Digital Signal Processor (DSP) to deliver superb audio performance - two dedicated to driving mids, another two dedicated to deliver the high frequencies, and one dedicated to churn out heart-pounding bass. The result? You’ll be able to hear all the details that other speakers fail to deliver. Together with its game-changing tri-amplified design with a total output of 75RMS/150W, the Katana truly is most powerful in its class. #SetupGoals are now achievable with the Katana. Comes equipped with comprehensive connectivity connections, the Katana is versatile and compatible with many multimedia devices.

If you are using multiple programs at the same time, the more RAM you will need. Will upgrading RAM improve performance? More RAM you have, the more applications you can have open simultaneously. What does a RAM upgrade do? With faster RAM, you increase the speed at which memory transfers information to other components. Meaning, your fast processor now has an equally fast way of talking to the other components, making your computer much more efficient. title: Club 3D CAC-1080 DisplayPort 1.4 to HDMI 2.0B HDR Adapter Supports 4096X2160@60Hz High Dynamic Range
categories: Electronics,Computers & Accessories,Computer Accessories & Peripherals,Computer Cable Adapters,DVI-HDMI Adapters
description: The Club3D CAC-1080 is a DisplayPort 1.4 To HDMI 2.0B active signal converter. It features support for HDR video quality for deep Color media content playback. The DisplayPort receiver supports up to 5, 4 Gbps per lane over 4 lanes. The HDMI output is fully compliant to HDMI specification version 2.0a, It supports RGB/YCbCr video color formats with a color depth of 16bpc (or 48 bits per Pixel) as long as it fits within the DisplayPort and HDMI link bandwidth. The CAC-1080 also supports Pixel encoding conversion from YCbCr 4: 2: 0 To YCbCr 4: 2: 0 pass-trough function. In addition HDR with deep color up to 12bpc at 4K 60Hz is supported through the conversion of RGB/YCbCr 4: 4: 4 over DP link to YCbCr 4: 2: 0 on the HDMI output with a horizontal expansion to CEA timings.

description: Product Description Plantronics Voyager PRO HD Over-the-ear with Smart Sensor technology redefines hands-free convenience, so you can answer calls simply by putting it on. Apps that offer tips, tricks and tools for your Android-based phone, brilliant HD audio and superior comfort make this the smartest headset for smartphones. Amazon.com The Plantronics Voyager PRO HD with Smart Sensor technology redefines hands-free convenience. This headset is so smart, that by simply placing it on your ear, it automatically answers your phone or transfers calls back and forth between your phone and headset. The Voyager PRO HD also boasts award-winning sound quality, noise cancellation, and three layers of wind noise reduction technology to ensure that your voice is heard clearly regardless of the sort of environment you're in. The Plantronics Voyager Pro HD (view larger). Ergonomic all-day fit (view larger). The Voyager PRO HD takes you beyond the headset, with the Plantronics MyHeadset app that gives you tips, tricks and tools for Android-based phones, combined with HD streaming audio plus natural sound and superior comfort and you've got the smartest headset for smartphones.Key FeaturesRevolutionary Smart Sensor technology manages your calls and automatically performs time-saving functions Experience brilliant, HD streaming audio plus natural, clear callsStreams music, podcasts, GPS directions, and other audio Up to 6 hours of talk time, up to 120 hours (5 days) of standby timeVoice alerts announce talk time, volume, connection and more Monitor your headset battery level on your iPhone or Android (3.0 or higher) smartphone Plantronics MyHeadset app for Android-based phones Smart Sensor TechnologyMaking and receiving calls is simpler with Smart Sensor technology in the Voyager PRO HD. The headset knows when you are wearing it so it cleverly routes calls to the headset when it's on your ear and to the handset when it's not. The Voyager PRO HD also has a locking call mechanism when it is not worn to eliminate accidental calling, and you can answer incoming calls simply by putting the headset on your ear--no buttons to press, applications to open or voice commands required. And if you are listening to music or other audio taking off the headset will automatically pause the stream. The Voyager PRO HD also features enhanced voice alerts that announce remaining talk time, connection status, battery-level, and mute. Smart Sensor technology knows whether to send calls to your mobile phone or your headset (view larger). WindSmart Noise-Canceling TechnologiesWindSmart technology incorporates enhanced stainless steel windscreens and GORE acoustic vents, as well as an electronic filter within the mic circuitry, making call audio clearer and sound more natural.Use Multipoint One Call at a TimeOnce you have activated multipoint and paired your two phones, it's easy to answer calls from either phone. When already on a call, you will hear a ringtone notification of the incoming call from the second paired phone.To answer a second call from the other phone, you must end the current call (tap Call button) so new call automatically answers. If you choose not to answer the second call, it will go to voicemail. See larger image. Get the most from your Plantronics headset with apps for AndroidThe MyHeadset app will do a sound check and familiarize you with the added functionality of your headset, such as streaming music.One touch conference call connectionInstantMeeting automatically identifies conference calls and dialing details from your calendar, reminds you just before the meeting is scheduled to begin, and, with one touch, connects you to your conference call.SpecificationsBluetooth version: 2.1 Bluetooth profiles: Advanced Audio Distribution (A2DP), Audio/Video Remote Control (AVRCP), Hands-free v1.5 (HFP), Headset v1.1 (HSP), Secure Simple Pairing (SSP) Charging connector: Micro USB Talk time: Up to 6 hours Standby time: Up to 5 days Service and support: 1-year limited warranty What's in the BoxPlantronics Voyager PRO HD headset, three sizes of ear tips, charger, USB cable, operating instructions

We are proud to call the cultural melting pot of Melbourne our creative base. Using business for good We are a certified B Corp, rated highly for limiting our impact on the environment, campaigning for the welfare of animals and donating a portion of our revenue to effective charities. Sustainable materials Our leathers come from the highest rated tanneries in the world -- as good as we can get for our products and the environment. And we are committed to pursuing recycled woven fabrics that keep excess plastics out of landfill.

title: Vivitar 3-Piece Multi-Coated HD Filter Set (40.5mm UV/CPL/ND8)
description: This Vivitar 3-Piece Filter Set contains a variety of multi-coated glass filters that will optimize your photography experience, and protect your lenses from scratches and dust. The UV (ultraviolet) filter removes and absorbs UV rays, giving sharper contrast to your images, and minimizing the bluish cast often found in daylight conditions. The CPL (circular polarizer) filter is often used to increase the contrast and saturation in blue skies and white clouds, while not affecting the overall color balance of a shot. It is also useful for reducing reflections on glass surfaces and bodies of water. The ND (neutral density) filter reduces intensity of all wavelengths or colors of light equally, giving no changes in hue or color rendition. ND filters are particularly useful reducing depth of field in very bright light. ND8 allows 1/8 of available light into the lens (3 f-stops).

title: PERLESMITH Full Motion TV Wall Mount for 37-82 inch TVs up to 132 lbs, Max VESA 600x400mm, TV Bracket with Dual Articulating Arms, Tilt, Swivel, Extension, 16" Wood Studs, PSLFK1
categories: Electronics,Television & Video,Accessories,TV Mounts, Stands & Turntables,TV Wall & Ceiling Mounts
description: About this item Universal TV Wall Mount: Full motion tv wall mount fits most 37”-82” TVs with VESA patterns 200x100mm to 600x400mm. Please verify the VESA pattern of your TV before purchase. Includes standard mounting hardware for easy installation. Wall mount bracket is compatible with most brands including Samsung, LG, TCL, Vizio, Sony, Panasonic, Toshiba, Sharp, Philips, JVC and more. Strong and Sturdy: The dual articulating arms of this swivel and tilt tv wall mount are made with high-strength steel to support up to 132 lbs of weight. Compatible with 12”-16” wood studs, concrete, and brick wall mounting. Enhanced Viewing Experience: The 65 inch TV wall mount bracket features +5°/-15° tilt to reduce glare, +/-60° swivel, and +/-3° leveling after installation. Easily optimize your viewing angle no matter where you are in the room. Save Space: By extending up to 16.14" and retracting to 2.8" from the wall when not in use, this TV wall mount for 75+ inch tv screens is an effective way to save space by freeing up floor space for placing speakers and gaming devices. description: Read more Slim housing frame in attractive design. 24.1” @ 16:10 aspect ratio with 1920x1200 resolution Huge color gamut with 99% Adobe RGB coverage Corner-to-corner brightness & color consistency - patented Digital Uniformity Equalizer technology Accurate colors & smooth gradations thanks to hardware calibration with external calibration device. and combined with built-in 16-bit LUT and external calibration device From the manufacturer Outstanding image quality for sharp, accurate images The screen impresses with its anti-reflective finish & WUXGA 1920x1200 resolution, a very good contrast ratio of 1,000:1, & a max brightness of 350 cd/m2. You can edit graphics & images pixel-accurately. And, text contours are clear and precise. The wide gamut (99% AdobeRGB) IPS LCD panel allows 178 degree viewing angles, thus keeping color tones & contrast accurately in the user's vision cone. Read more Wide Gamut - ideal for raw images and printing If you work with RAW or AdobeRGBimages, you will love this Wide Gamut Monitor. The large color space reproduces 99% of the AdobeRGBcolor gamut. If images taken in RAW format are converted to AdobeRGB, the monitor will represent these correctly. So you can see a bright blue sky and rich green forests in lifelike color - unlike monitors with sRGB color gamut. But even when printing, the EIZO monitor offers significant advantages: It covers almost the entire CMYK press color space (e.g., ISO Coated and U.S. Web Coated). You can accurately predict on the screen what the print will look like and dramatically reduce the number and cost of proofs. Read more Constant tone value across the entire screen Pixel by pixel, EIZO’s patented Digital Uniformity Equalizer (DUE) adjusts all tone values across the entire monitor. The effect: The colors appear identical at every point of the screen, with no variations in brightness compared to conventional LCDs. The CS2420 also balances the effects of fluctuations in ambient temperature on color temperature and brightness. You can enjoy a uniform color and luminance distribution across the screen. A big plus for photo retouching. Read more Professional calibration with EIZO ColorNavigator. Accurate image processing is only achieved on well-calibrated monitors. Typical monitor software calibration takes a long time and requires expertise from the user. The CS2420 comes with ColorNavigator hardware calibration software. It can be carried out in just a few simple steps, even by users without deep technical knowledge. Advanced users can set brightness, gamma, white point, and other calibration settings as target values numerically. Because the calibration takes place through the hardware of the monitor, it is lossless and independent of computer and graphics card. The CS2730 fits perfectly into an existing system. Our EX4 external calibration sensor can be ordered as an optional add-on with the CS2420. Read more EIZO microchip for optimum colour reproduction. The CS2420 includes a custom-designed microchip (ASIC, Application-Specific Integrated Circuit), which EIZO has specially developed for the special requirements of professional colorwork. With its own algorithm, EIZO ASICs ensure precise, uniform, and consistent color representation. 10-bit color depth: one billion colors in the finest gradation. Thanks to a 10-bit color representation based on a 16-bit LUT, you can use a huge color spectrum. Over a billion colors are available on the screen at the same time. That's 64 times as many colors as a standard 8-bit display. Color gradations are finer and the spacing between adjacent colors lower, which means gradation banding is reduced or totally eliminated. Also important or post-production: The extended greyscale range. 10-bit image input providesup to 14% more grayscale range. High-resolution look-up table. With its 16-bit look-up table, the CS2420 draws from a table of 278 trillion colors, ensuring an accurate view of your image’s color. Dark color values, color nuances, and image structure are retained. This reliable and precise reproduction reduces correction steps and thus shortens valuable production time. Read more

title: BTECH QHM22D Dual Push-to-Talk (PTT) Speaker Mic, Platinum Series IP54 Rainproof Shoulder Mic for BaoFeng, BTECH, Kenwood Radios
categories: Electronics,Portable Audio & Video,CB & Two-Way Radios,Accessories,Headsets & Microphones
description: BTECH has introduced its Platinum Series Heavy Duty Speaker Mic. This Speaker Mic (QHM22D) is the "HEAVY DUTY" version speaker mic you have been looking for! Compared to other BaoFeng mics this one is designed in the USA for construction sites, industrial use and for all rough assignments. It is built with an impact resistant PVC casing (IP54), for Shock, wind, dust, and splash resistance. It is a High quality microphone with Crystal clear audio Includes a heavy duty stainless steel clips on lapel. You're free to talk without holding your radio. (with 8 adjustable positions) Dual Push-To-Talk (PTT) Speaker Mic Designed for the UV-82 series radios (GMRS-V1, MURS-V1, UV-82HP, UV-82C, and other UV-82 series models) The speaker mic includes dual push to talk buttons to operate with compatible radios (it is backwards compatible as a single PTT speaker mic with single push-to-talk radios) . Speaker microphone Heavy Duty (built in 3.5 mm miniature earphone jack) for listen only earpiece Dual PTT Features: Has a remote microphone with Dual push to talk button - don't mix up your conversations - the buttons coordinate with your display (on compatible UV-82 series radios)! The upper / top button will access the upper frequency, while the lower / side button will access the lower frequency on your radio.Package Includes: *QHM22D Heavy Duty Speaker MicCompatible Radio Models: BTECH: DMR-6X2, UV-5X3, GMRS-V1, MURS-V1 BaoFeng BF-F8HP, UV-5R Series, BF-888S, UV-3R+, UV-82C, UV-82HP, UV-82 Series AnyTone AT-D878UV TYT MD-380, TYT MD-390, TYT radios with Kenwood 2 Pin Standard Arcshell AR-5, AR-6 Retevis H-777, RT-21 Radioddity GD-77 Kenwood Connector Compatible: All radios with the 2-pin K1 type connector (found in Wouxun, Arcshell, Kenwood, and other brands)

unprecedented combination of USB connectivity, universal drive bays, and advanced SoftRAID capabilities into a whisper-quiet aluminum enclosure. Whatever your workflow needs, the Mercury Elite Pro Quad has the flexibility to take your storage capacity, performance, and data security to a whole new level. The Flexibility of USB-C The Mercury Elite Pro Quad's powerful USB-C interface delivers 10Gb/s USB 3.1 Gen 2 bandwidth and works with any USB-C or Thunderbolt 3 equipped Mac or Windows PC. Simply connect the Mercury Elite Pro Quad via the included USB-C cable to experience next-level performance. If your computer doesn't feature USB-C connectivity, the included USB-C to USB-A cable brings backward compatibility for machines with legacy USB ports. Capacity without Compromise Compatible with 2.5" and 3.5" drives, the Mercury Elite Pro Quad's four universal drive bays let users pack up to a massive 48TB of storage. With this level of capacity and drive flexibility, you will not have to compromise when it comes to your storage. Speed, Storage, and Security with SoftRAID The Mercury Elite Pro Quad features advanced RAID capabilities, letting you choose the best option for your workflow. Whether you want massive capacity through a single large array, need maximum performance up to 947MB/s, or redundancy to keep your data secure, the Mercury Elite Pro Quad gives you the power of choice with OWC's proprietary SoftRAID engine or Windows-supported RAID modes. The Mercury Elite Pro Quad is also available in a RAID-ready model so you can install the RAID software of your choice. Designed for Professionals by Professionals Every detail was considered when designing the Mercury Elite Pro Quad. Built with a heat-dissipating aluminum enclosure, a whisper-quiet fan, and vibration-absorbing feet, the Mercury Elite Pro Quad runs cool and quietly, making it ideal for noise-sensitive environments. Front-facing LEDs provide an instant drive-activity snapshot, while the front panel access lock keeps your drives safe. You can even secure the entire drive with the rear-mounted Kensington compatible lock slot. On top of that, drive-equipped models undergo OWC's multi-hour drive "burn-in" performance certification procedure to ensure that your drive arrives operating properly and ready to perform. Reliability and Support You Can Count On Like all OWC drives, the Mercury Elite Pro Quad is built to the highest standards of reliability and performance. Because 100% reliability is always the goal, Mercury Elite Pro Quad is rigorously quality tested, and backed by OWC 24/7 customer support. Q: Why can I see nothing when I start the system? A: Please operate as below: Step 1, Check NVR if it has electricity, user can check mouse lamp, Ethernet port and so on, we suggest use NVR standard power. You can keep pressing Right mouse button for more than 10 seconds and NVR output resolution will be set to 1024x768. title: 150' Feet, White RG6 Coaxial Cable (Coax Cable) with Weather Proof Connectors, F81 / RF, Digital Coax - AV, Cable TV, Antenna, and Satellite, CL2 Rated, 150 Foot
description: THE CIMPLE CO, A Family Company located in the USA, is proud to manufacture this high quality and durable coaxial cable. This cable is available in Black and White, and comes in lengths from 1 foot to 200 feet (including our most popular lengths of 6 feet, 15 feet, 25 feet, 30 feet, 50 feet, and 100 feet). The center conductor is made of high grade copper coated steel that has been swept to 3.0GHz, making this a great application for Satellite, Cable, Wireless (including cell services), and Communication uses. With very low signal attenuation (2.75dB at 750MHz for our 50' cable) it can be used on long runs without the loss of signal or picture. We use high grade 360 degree compression connectors to ensure that this cable remains water and weather proof, without the loss of any signal. This ensures that the ends can withstand pulling, weather, extreme hot and cold (rated up to 167 degrees F). The coaxial shielding is 80% aluminum magnesium alloy braid and 100% solid aluminum foil (including an 18% overlap) to ensure that there is no interference from neighboring or rouge signals. The outer jacket is a flexible UV resistant PVC and has been tested to be used in many extreme conditions for use both inside and outside. The dielectric center is made from gas injected foam PE and has an almost perfect consistency of 75 Ohms +/-3 throughout the entire length of the coax cable. The outside diameter of the cable is 0.27 inches, about 6.85 mm, with the connectors being slightly larger at .4375 (7/16) of an inch (11.11 mm). The cable also has length markings every two feet on the side to make it easier to cut to length, if you need a shorter wire. We also offer a repair and splice kit for those who would like to cut and reinstall the ends on the wire. The kit comes complete with instructions and free technical support. We back our product 100%, with free returns, as well as free technical and customer support.

description: HighPoint’s SSD7140A high port count (HPC) NVMe RAID controller is ideal for professional applications that require a small-footprint, mass-storage M.2 NVMe solution that can take full advantage of PCIe 3.0 x16 transfer bandwidth, and deliver over 14,000MB/s of transfer performance.The SSD7140A doubles M.2 port count from 4 to eight, and can support up to 32TB of storage capacity.Truly Platform Independent NVMe RAID Solution: Unlike most NVMe devices in today’s marketplace, which are tied to a specific hardware platform or brand of SSD or motherboard, SSD7000 series controllers do not require a hardware environment with Bifurcation support, or any specialized software released by SSD manufacturers; any AMD or Intel motherboard with a dedicated PCIe 3.0 x16 slot can now support up to 8 M.2 NVMe SSDs, and experience sustained transfer performance in excess of 14GB/s via a single compact PCIe device.Comprehensive 8-Port M.2 NVMe RAID & Storage Solution: RAID 1/0 (Security & Speed) - RAID 1/0 (also known as RAID 10) requires a minimum of 4 NVMe SSD’s – it will mirror the data of one stripe array to a second, hidden stripe array for security. RAID 0 (Speed) – this mode delivers Maximum Performance, and requires a minimum of 2 NVMe SSD’s. RAID 1 (Security) - This mode creates a hidden duplicate of the target SSD, and requires 2 NVMe SSD’s to configure. Ultra-Efficient, Multi-Stage Cooling Solution: The SSD7140A employs our new ultra-efficient, multi-stage cooling-solution that combines a high-conductivity thermal pad with an anodized aluminum heatsink equipped with dual built-in, low noise fans. This design ensures the M.2 SSDs, NVMe chipset and RAID componentry remain cool, even under heavy load, while minimizing the risk of distraction in the work environment.Comprehensive NVMe RAID Management: The Web RAID Management Interface (WebGUI) is a simple, intuitive web-based management tool and is ideal for customers who are new to RAID technology. The CLI (command line interface) is a powerful, text-only management interface designed for advanced users and professional administrators. Customers can easily track TBW (Terabytes Written) and the temperature of each individual NVMe SSD, ensure the SSD7000 controller is using the fastest available PCIe slot, configure an event log with email notification, and monitor the status of critical RAID configurations in person or remotely via an internet connection.

They are approved for use on Coaxial Cables, Cat5 Cables, and similar communication lines - as they will not crush or distort the signal. Rated at 50lb / 222n Tensile Strength, these ties do not break easily and are designed to last. They hold great amounts of weight.

title: Premium Car Headrest Tablet Mount and Back Seat iPad Car Holder, Jarv [Multi Passenger] Telescopic Fold-Up Rear Seat Tablet Holder for Car Headrest - iPad PRO iPad Air iPad Mini (All 7-18” Tablets)
description: The prefect companion to help alleviate some of the tension we experience in a road trip     The mount features Jarv's headrest clamp base, which easily attaches onto most 2-post style headrests on either the front or back seats with an included Allen wrench. An adjustable double-ball robust mount pedestal connects the base to the slim grip tablet holder, which features a spring-loaded quick release design that makes it easy to insert or remove the tablet by pushing down on the lower legs with one hand. Compatible for use with: iPad Pro 12.9" (2021 2020 2018 2017) A2462 A2379 A2378 A2233 A2232 A2229 A2069 A2014 A1983 A1895 A1876 A1821 A1671 A1670 A1652 A1584 iPad Pro 11" (2021 2020 2018) A2460 A2377 A2301 A2231 A2230 A2228 A2068 A2013 A1980 A1979 A1934 iPad Pro 10.5" (2017) A1852 A1709 A1701 iPad Pro 9.7" (2016) A1675 A1674 A1673 iPad Air 4 3 2 1 (2020 2019 2014 2013) A2325 A2324 A2316 A2154 A2153 A2152 A2123 A2072 A1567 A1566 A1476 A1475 A1474 iPad 8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1 (2019 2018 2017 2012 2012 2011 2010) A2430 A2429 A2428 A2270 A2200 A2198 A2197 A1954 A1893 A1823 A1822 A1460 A1459 A1458 A1430 A1416 A1397 A1396 A1395 A1337 A1219 Samsung Galaxy Tab A7 Lite Wi-Fi \ A7 Lite LTE \ LTE \ A7 Wi-Fi \ A 4G \ A Wi-Fi \ A 10.5 Wi-Fi \ A 10.5 4G Samsung Galaxy Tab S7 FE LTE \ S7 Wi-Fi \ S7+ Wi-Fi \ S6 Lite Wi-Fi \ S6 Lite 4G \ S6 \ S5e Wi-Fi Samsung Galaxy Tab A8 Lite Wi-Fi \ A8 Lite LTE \ LTE \ A8 Wi-Fi \ A 4G \ A Wi-Fi \ A 10.5 Wi-Fi \ A 10.5 4G Samsung Galaxy Tab S8 FE LTE \ S8 Wi-Fi \ S8+ Wi-Fi \ S8 Lite Wi-Fi \ S8 Lite 4G \ S8 \ S5e Wi-F Fire HD10 Fire HD10 Pus Fire HD8 Fire HD8 Plus Fire HD8 Kids and Fire 7 (2022) ROAD WARRIOR:       VIEWING ANGLES: Swivel ball connection with full 360 degree rotation with tilt mechanism, is ideal and offers optimal viewing while in both portrait or landscape mode COMPATIBILITY: Universal headrest tablet mount will function fully with all tablet display sizes that range from 7-18 inches and can be used with or without a carrying case ENTERTAINMENT SYSTEM: Backseat tablet holder mount transforms your tablet, portable DVD player, laptop or hybrid PC into a perfect in-car entertainment solution BACKSEAT ENTERTAINMENT:         STORED AWAY: Our multi viewing headrest mount can slide in place, fold up and be easily tucked away when not in use PACKAGE CONTENTS: 10 support legs (4 short, 2 medium and 4 long versions). choose the 4 legs that provide the best fit for your tablet. These insert at the top and bottom of the holder and can be easily adjusted and will keep all ports unobstructed. For large tablets, the best configuration is to attach 2 short support legs on top and the 2 long support legs on the bottom. For smaller tablets, use all 4 short support legs VIBRATION-FREE: Our tablet holder can bear weight of 40 lb without tilting forward , and can still remain stable on bumpy roads without shaking or vibrating

title: Hikity 8 Core 4G+64G Android 12 Car Stereo Double Din Wireless Apple Carplay Android Auto, 9" IPS Screen Car Audio Bluetooth, GPS Navi, WiFi, Mirrror Link, 36EQ DSP, FM RDS, SWC + Mic, Backup Cam
categories: Electronics,Car & Vehicle Electronics,Car Electronics,Car Video,In-Dash Navigation
description: Hikity 8 Core 4+64GB Android 12 Car Radio with Wireless Carplay Android Auto Mirror Link 9 Inch Touchscreen System: Android 12.0 Chip: 7250B Chipset: 8 cores Operating speed: 2.0 GHz Screen size: 9'' Screen resolution: 1280*720 Memory: 4GB (RAM) + 64GB (ROM) Power output: 4*45W Amplifier: ST7851L Radio chip: 8035 Working voltage: 9V～16V Intelligent Voice: Support Bluetooth version: 5.0 USB: Dual USB ports Digital Signal Processor: Support   Android 12 with Powerful 8 Core High-quaality processor enables a fastly smooth spped, providing a wonderful using experience.4GB RAM and 64GB ROM Support more security features, massive memory, advanced ultra-fast storage, and intuitive control needed for lag-free workflow.Built-in WiFi Equipped with WiFi connection, which allowing driver to download various apps on the radio. You are support to surf the web as well, making it more convenient for you.   Wired and Wireless Apple Carplay & Android Auto Support Iphone and Android mobile phone for Apple Carplay and Android Auto function. By connecting to the car radio via original USB data cable/Bluetooth with a built-in app 'Zlink5', it is easily to access this function.Support voice control. By saying 'Hey siri' or 'Ok Google', driver easily access to map navigation, notification, email, phone contacts, music, video and etc, giving you a safer and more efficient driving experience.   The 9 inch double din touchscreen car stereo support Iphone and Andreroid phone for Mirror Link function. By connecting your phone, the big touchscreen can synchronously display the content of your phone to the radio, giving you a wonderful experience. Huawei and Samsung phone are not supported.       GPS Navigation Built-in navigation app provides real-time road conditions, helping avoid traffic jams. After connecting to the WiFi, you can download the map you need on the app, and you can enjoy offline navigation next time. Steering Wheel Control Function The double din car radio supports steering wheel control. After completing the steering wheel button learning, you can control the Bluetooth radio through the steering wheel, making driving easier and safer. Three Split Screen Supporting split screen, driver supported to use GPS navigation and watch video at the same time on the radio, making it much convenient.       36EQ DSP With DSP tuning technology, you can adjust frequency, AE, 36 band EQ, 10 band EQ, sound type selection on the APP to make up for the lack of original speakers and get better lossless sound quality. FM/RDS Radio High-quality FM/RDS radio that supports automatic channel search and online listening to news, weather, traffic information, etc. Support saving 18 radio stations. Bluetooth 5.0 The car audio receiver with built-in bluetooth 5.0 supports bluetooth hands-free calling, bluetooth music playback and automatic loading of the phone book.

title: KECC Compatible with MacBook Air 13 inch Case 2022 2021 2020 Release A2337 M1 A2179 Retina Display + Touch ID Protective Plastic Hard Shell + Keyboard Cover (Rainbow Mist 2)
categories: Electronics,Computers & Accessories,Laptop Accessories,Bags, Cases & Sleeves,Hard Shell Cases
description: IMPORTANT: PLEASE READ BEFORE PURCHASING!! WARNING: Before you make payment, PLEASE ENSURE YOU CHECK YOUR MACBOOK MODEL NUMBER IN ORDER TO CHOOSE THE CORRECT SIZE CASE FOR YOUR MACBOOK. For those who are unfamiliar, there are different variants of MacBook notebook over the years. There are 3 versions of MacBook Pro 13 cases and 2 versions of MacBook Pro 15 cases which we are selling on Amazon. Therefore it is extremely important that you have selected the correct size (model number) so that you will receive the correct case for your MacBook. How to check your MacBook model number: The model number is located on the back of your MacBook, in small prints which says "Model: A1XXX" . "XXX" are numerical numbers. Model Numbers: MacBook Air 13'' Retina (2020 / 2019 / 2018 version, with Touch ID) : A2337 M1/A2179 / A1932 MacBook Pro 13" (2022 / 2021 / 2020 / 2019 / 2018 / 2017 / 2016 version) : M2,A2338 M1,A2289, A2251, A2159, A1989, A1706 (with Touch Bar) / A1708 (without Touch Bar) MacBook Pro 16" (2020 / 2019 version) : A2141 Old MacBook Air 13" (no Touch ID) : A1466 / A1369 Old MacBook Pro 13" with Retina Display (2012 - 2015 version) : A1502 / A1425 Old MacBook Pro 13" with CD Drive (2009 - 2012 version) : A1278 MacBook Pro 15" (2019 / 2018 / 2017 / 2016 version) : A1990 / A1707 Old MacBook Pro 15" with Retina Display (2012-2015 version) : A1398 MacBook 12" : A1534 MacBook Air 11" : A1465 / A1370   Premium Quality and Design, Over 100 Colors to Choose From Premium Quality - KECC MacBook Hard Shell Case contains a layer of Rubber Oil Paint for a Smooth Rubberized Exterior Texture, which prevents Fingerprints, Slipping, Scratches, Drops, Dirt, Smudges and Other Damages.Cut Out Design - Logo Shines through the case.Multiple Styles - Over 100 Colors, Materials and Bundles to choose from, there is always an option for you and your family/friends.   Easy Carry and Access Full access to all ports and drives, plug your charger, headphones, hard drive without removing the case.Ultra Slim and Light Weight - The ultra slim design of the case make it easy to carry inside your bag, it does not add a lot of weight which is very accessible to bring it outside.   Maximum Heat Ventilation Bottom Case has a unique design with two rows of bottom ventilation, allowing safe heat disbursement, helping your MacBook to stay cool in hot temperatures.Four anti-slip silicone feet keeps your MacBook firmly in place, create a thin layer of air between your MacBook and the surface for extra heat ventilation Case Features       Full Protection Offers the laptop better protection and safety, protecting your laptop from Fingerprints, Slipping, Scratches, Drops, Dirt, Smudges and Other Damages. Two pieces Design Two piece folio design, easily clips onto your MacBook with upper and bottom cover. Custom Made KECC Hard Shell Case is Custom Made for your MacBook with Full Access to All Ports, Plug in your Charger, Headphones, Hard drive without removing the bottom case.

title: Canon VIXIA HF G50 4K30P Camcorder, Black
description: Seeing is believing–and with 4K capabilities in the VIXIA HF G50 camcorder, you'll be seeing everything more dramatically, more intensely and more realistically. Detail and color reign supreme with the large-format CMOS Sensor, which combines with the DIGIC DV 6 Image Processor to deliver brilliant results on any screen. An advanced 20x Optical Zoom lens gives you impressive telephoto power and a wide angle of view, while the 5-axis Image Stabilization system provides the steadiness and focus you need for your productions. With 4K resolution, amazing features and a mobile-friendly design, the VIXIA HF G50 gives you stunning video quality on the go.

description: Product Description A handy replacement for a lost cable, or a nice spare for the office. This cable provides a transfer rate up to 480 Mbps depending upon the peripheral's USB version, and is ideal for transferring pictures from your digital camera to your PC or Mac. Foil and braid shielding reduces EMI/RFI interference and twisted pair construction helps reduce crosstalk thus ensuring high speed, error-free data transfer. Amazon.com The future of computer connectivity has arrived with this mini-USB cable from Cables to Go. The fully rated universal serial bus cable provides transfer rates of up to 480 Mbps and easily connects any 5-pin mini-USB device--including cell phones, PDAs, digital cameras, and MP3 players--to the USB port on your hub, PC, or Mac. The cable comes with foil and braid shielding to reduce electromagnetic and radio frequency interference, along with a twisted-pair construction that helps reduce crosstalk, thus ensuring high-speed, error-free data transfer time and again. As with all Cables to Go products, the cable also meets the UL requirements for communication cabling and is compatible with USB 1.0, 1.1, and 2.0 versions. title: TrickleStar TS1810 Tier II A/V Aps+ 7 Outlet Advanced Powerstrip+, Multi-Sensor, Save Energy, Reduce Active and Standby Power Consumed, Premium Fireproof Surge Protection
categories: Electronics,Accessories & Supplies,Power Strips & Surge Protectors,Power Strips
description: Product Description The TrickleStar 7-outlet AV Advanced PowerStrip Plus is an energy-saving surge protector that saves you money by reducing active and standby power waste in your home entertainment system. ​ Active power waste occurs when the TV is left on and no one is watching it, whereas standby power waste is energy consumed by AV electronic equipment even after you turn them off.​​ The AV Advanced PowerStrip Plus reduces active power waste by switching off the TV when not in use and cuts standby power waste by removing supplied power to peripheral electronic equipment. How it Works Featuring a highly-accurate sensor, the AV Advanced PowerStrip Plus detects remote control signals and motion in the room to determine whether the TV is being used. If no remote control activity or motion is detected within the countdown timer period, the AV Advanced PowerStrip Plus automatically powers down the TV and AV peripheral electronics plugged into the switched outlets, saving you money and energy. Key Benefits Saves energy and reduces electricity costs by automatically powering down the TV and AV electronics when left on and not in use Eliminates standby power waste by removing supplied power to AV peripheral electronics (e.g., DVD player, AV receiver, speakers) Features a visual flashing LED and an audible chirp notification to effectively alert you prior to powering down electronics Premium-quality, fireproof surge protection safeguards electronic equipment against dangerous surge spikes Improves video and sound quality of connected electronics by filtering out electromagnetic and radio-frequency interference Reduces active & standby power waste in AV entertainment systems Designed to save energy by reducing active and standby power waste in audiovisual (AV) home entertainment systems, the AV Advanced PowerStrip Plus monitors remote control activity and motion to determine device usage, and it automatically switches off the TV and AV peripheral electronics when left on and not in use. Read more Intelligent multi-sensing technology ensures proper shutdown of AV electronics A highly-accurate multi-sensor that connects to the power strip detects IR remote control signals and motion from the moment you power on your television. If you leave the TV on, the sensor will detect a lapse in remote control activity and user presence (motion). When no activity is detected within the countdown period (configurable to 1 or 2 hours), the TV and AV peripheral electronics automatically power down, saving you money and energy. Read more Premium-quality, fireproof surge protection safeguards electronics from surges TrickleStar's surge protector products incorporate advanced surge protection technology with ceramic-encased Metal Oxide Varistors that suppress more energy and dissipate heat faster than traditional surge protection products. The ceramic casing is fireproof and therefore capable of preventing fire during abnormal surge conditions. Read more Key Benefits: Reduces active and standby power waste This energy-savvy surge protector reduces power waste by automatically switching off the TV and AV peripheral electronics when not in use. Accurately determines if AV electronics are in use The connected multi-sensor detects IR remote control signals and motion to accurately determine whether the TV and AV electronics are being used. Compatible with all types of televisions Advanced power measurement and auto-threshold detection ensure compatibility with all types of televisions. Effective visual & audible alert notifications A flashing LED notification and optional piezo buzzer (soft audible chirp) alert user prior to powering down electronics Read more Feature Diagram: 15 Amp resettable circuit breaker Heavy-duty power cord with an angled, space-saver plug Surge/ground/switched status LED indicators 1,080 Joules of premium-quality, fireproof surge protection <40 dB EMI/RFI noise filtering Two always-on outlets Five switched (energy-saving) outlets with one current-sensing for the TV Child protective outlet covers Multi-sensor that detects IR remote control signals and motion Flashing LED and audible piezo buzzer notification Manual on/off button for switched outlets 8-foot cable

Bi-color LED indicators The Zyxel GS-105S v2 features auto-sensing function and Gigabit Ethernet ports with easy-to-understand LED indicators, which allows users to quickly check link and activity status at a glance. Perfectly fulfilling the demands for multimedia streaming and online gaming. Green Ethernet for energy saving Compliant with the IEEE 802.3az Energy Efﬁcient Ethernet standard as “Green Ethernet”, the Zyxel GS-105S v2 provides power-saving beneﬁts without compromising performance. The GS-105S v2 automatically detects power consumption according to the number of active connected network devices and cable length. When fewer active connected network devices or shorter Ethernet cable length, the switches will consume less power accordingly. Fanless design Extend your network without disrupting your quiet home environment. This switch features a fanless design that ensures noiseless operation and greater reliability over time with no moving parts that may fail.

a depth of 30ft/10m PVC-free made from thin, ultra-clear TPU Aquapac Classic Waterproof VHF Radio Case - IPX8 - Large 225x400mm - Grey/Clear A waterproof, submersible radio case that protects your radio against the elements whilst enabling you to use it through the case. It also protects waterproof radios from corrosion and makes them buoyant! Our Aquaclip seal keeps your radio safe with IPX8 Submersible protection against continuous immersion to a depth of 30ft/10m. PVC-free, this case is constructed from tough, ultra-clear TPU with clear windows on both sides. Whatever adventure you’re seeking, immerse yourself with Aquapac. IPX8 Standard Protection — Submersible At Aquapac we use an internationally recognised standard of waterproofing — the IPX scale, ranging from IPX0 (no protection) to IPX8 (protection against continuous immersion). IPX8 is defined as protection against continuous immersion to a depth of 30ft/10m — and we call this Submersible. Sealed with our patented Aquaclip This radio case is sealed with our patented Aquaclip, an ultra-secure, rustproof, plastic seal that fully protects your radio from submersion in deep water to 30ft/10m. description: Please Read before Purchase (1). A hard drive is NOT INCLUDED. You must separately purchase one with a capacity of your choice up to 8TB in size. We recommend using surveillance hard drive only. Other types of hard drives may cause your DVR to stutter, skip, freeze and will prematurely fail due to constant writing conditions.(2). This 4K NVR supports most other brands WIRED ip cameras that support ONVIF and RTSP protocol. Use only IP Cameras of equal or LOWER resolution than the maximum supported resolution of the NVR.(3). Since different suppliers use different protocols, we could only ensure the full compatibility (include motion detection function)between the Evtevision ip cameras and the Evtevision NVRs. For some third-party ip cameras that support ON VIF and RTSP protocol, we could support live view only.(4). If you want to remote viewing on smart phone, you would need to connect the internet to the nvr. Specifications of Evtevision 16CH 4K Network Video Recorder Video Compression H.265+ Video Input 16ch 4K Video Output 1ch HD output(max 4K)/1ch VGA(max 1080P) Audio Input/Output No audio input/1ch 3.5MM audio output Preview Resolution 16ch*4K Playback Resolution 4K/5M/4M/3M/1080P HDD Capacity Support 1 HDD up to 8TB (HDD not included) Network Interface 1 RJ45 10M/100M adaptive Ethernet port USB Interface 2* USB2.0 Operating Power DC12V Remote Operation(3G/4G/WiFi) Via http using IE & iPhone / iPad / Android / PC Client Record Mode Manual/Alarm/Motion detection/Timing Back up mode Network backup/USB hard disk/USB burner/SATA burner Package Content 1*NVR,1*DC12V Power Supply,1*USB Mouse,1*HDD Screws Bag     Smart Motion Detection Alert and APP Push By setting up smart motion detection,once any movement is detected by the security camera system, you will receive instant push notifications via Xmeye Pro App, email alerts and buzzer alarms, so you are able to act in the first time if something suspicious happens.   Simple DIY Installation Extra items (not included) you'll need to make the NVR work: Evtevision IP cameras, RJ45 cables, camera adapters, an HDD. Connect the IP cameras to the router with RJ45 cables, link the NVR to a router with network cable, power on the cameras & NVR and then get instant live view & 24/7 recording.   Advanced H.265+ Video Format Compared to H.264, H.265+ coding sends smaller file sizes while keeping high image quality. And has a longer recording time before overwriting.   Easy Local or Remote View from multiple devices Local Viewing: No Network needed, just connect the system to a monitor via HDMI / VGA port and enjoy multiple-cam views on one screen.Remote Viewing: Connect the internet to the NVR . Download the Xmeye Pro app on your smartphone, Or download the VMS PC client on PC. Does it come with cameras or hard disk? No, this item contains: 1×NVR & 1×Power Adapter & 1×USB Mouse & 1×User Manual & 1× HDD Screws kit . What should I do before adding the system to the APP? Before you add the system to the APP, please make your system is connected to the internet, it needs to use an Ethernet cable to connect it to the router. Why the motion detection does not work? This NVR supports live view with 3rd-party IP camera that support onvif protocol, and the motion function is fully compatible with Evtevision IP cameras only. I forgot the NVR admin password, what do i do? Reboot your NVR and retry typing your password 3 times from the DVR console with a monitor connected.The screen will display a QR code.Take a clear photo of the QR code and send it to us for a reply with a valid password.

title: MokerLink 8 Port 10Gbps SFP+ Switch, Support 1G SFP and 10G SFP+, 160Gbps Bandwidth, Fanless Unmanaged Plug and Play Ethernet Switch
description: Key Features: MokerLink 8 port 10G ethernet switch upgrading networks by providing a more reliable, stable, seamless network and easily multiplying the network speed by 10 times. It provides 8* 1G/10Gbps SFP+ ports with line speed forwarding capability per port. 8*10 Gigabit SFP+ optical ports are provided to realize line speed forwarding.Each port supports MDI/MDIX automatic flip and duplex / rate self negotiation.10000M base-t(x) automatic detection, full / half duplex MDI / mdi-x adaptive.   With 10 Gigabit speed, the 10G080GS brings high-flexibility and high-bandwidth connectivity to WIFI6 AP, router, servers, workstations and other attached devices. It enables you to save time when transferring large files. 12K jumbo frames are also supported to improve network utilization in large files transfer.       Full 10G Port The 10G080GS features non-blocking wire-speed architecture with 160Gbps switching capacity for maximum data throughput. It supports IEEE 802.3x flow control for full-duplex mode, and back pressure flow control for half-duplex mode alleviates traffic congestion and ensures reliable data transmission. An 16K MAC address table provides scalability for even the largest networks. Plug and Play This 8 port 10G switch support installation plug and play. No configuring is required. Auto MDI/MDI-X crossover on all ports eliminate the need for crossover cables or uplink ports. Auto-negotiation on each port senses the link speed of a network device (either 1G/10Gbps) and intelligently adjusts for compatibility and optimal performance. description: Meike 85mm f1.8 Full Frame Auto Focus Telephoto Lens for Canon EOS EF Mount   Meike 85mm f/1.8 Performance AF noisy and slow Works with : Canon EOS EF mount cameras, such as 1D 5D 5D3 5D4 7D Mark II 70D 80D 800D 1000D 1100D 600D 60D 450D 550D Rebel T7i T6i T6s T6 T5i T5 T4i T3i SL2 Digital SLR Camera etc Sharpness: very good level at f/1.8 and f/2.8, rising to excellent from f/4 to f/8. Sharpness is still very good at f/11 and f/16, only falling off to fair levels at f/22. Edge sharpness is quite poor at f/1.8, fair at f/2.8 but then perks up to being very good at f/4 and excellent at f/5.6 to f/8. It is still very good at f/11 and f/16, falling off to being only fair at f/22. CA (Chromatic Aberration) is remarkably well controlled throughout the aperture range. It is very unlikely that CA will be seen as a problem and if further correction is ever needed we can of course look to software solutions. Vignetting at open aperture is quite obvious at -1.5 stops, although this does have a useful side effect in that corners of an image are often darkened inpost processing to concentrate our eyes on the centre of the image. Here we have a natural effect, more often seen in wide angle designs. At f/2.8 darkening has reduced to around two thirds of a stop and this has reduced to about one third of a stop by f/4. It doesn't really get any better than this, the mild -0.3 stop vignetting continuing right through the aperture range. The lens shows +0.63% pincushion distortion, which again is an excellent performance. Further correction could be made in software if the need arose, but for most purposes this would not be necessary. Performance against the light is excellent as well, and flare was not observed in any of the conditions found throughout the test period. description: Product Description High performance and a compact design make the SEL-35F18 an ideal “second lens” that is easy to carry around when capturing the action. It’s ideal for a wide variety of photos, including snapshots while strolling, night shots (thanks to the bright maximum aperture) and portraits with superb background/foreground blur. Designed for use with: Hasselblad Lunar Sony PXW-FS5 Sony PXW-FS7 Sony PXW-FS7M2 Sony PXW-FS7M2K Sony Alpha A5000 Sony Alpha A5100 Sony Alpha A6000 Sony Alpha A6300 Sony Alpha A6500 Sony Alpha NEX-7 Sony Alpha a5100 Sony Handycam NEX-VG30 Sony NXCAM NEX-EA50M Sony XDCAM PXW-FS7 Sony Alpha a6500 Sony NEX-EA50M Sony NEX-EA50UH Sony NEX-FS700R Sony NEX-VG30 Sony NEX-VG900 Sony PXW-FS5 Sony PXW-FS5 Kit Sony PXW-FS5M2 Sony PXW-FS7 Sony PXW-FS7M2 Sony QX1 High performance and a compact design make the SEL-35F18 an ideal “second lens” that is easy to carry around when capturing the action. It’s ideal for a wide variety of photos, including snapshots while strolling, night shots (thanks to the bright maximum aperture) and portraits with superb background/foreground blur. When changing your aperture to defocus the background, the light sources appear blurred. This ‘bokeh’ effect of the blurred background can be enhanced with circular aperture blades used in this lens. Conventional aperture blades have flat sides creating unappealing polygonal shaped defocussed points of light. α lenses overcome this problem through a unique design that keeps the aperture almost perfectly circular from its wide-open setting to when it is closed by 2 stops. Smoother, more natural defocusing can be obtained as a result. As focal lengths get longer, lenses built with conventional optical glass have difficulties with chromatic aberration, and as a result images suffer from lower contrast, lower color quality, and lower resolution. ED glass dramatically reduces chromatic aberration at telephoto ranges, and provides superior contrast across the entire image, even at large aperture settings. Super ED glass provides enhanced compensation for chromatic aberration. Aspherical lens design dramatically reduces spherical aberration while also reducing lens size and weight. Spherical aberration is a slight misalignment of the light rays projected on the image plane. This is caused by differences in refraction at different points on conventional spherical lenses which degrade image quality in large-aperture lenses. Specially shaped “aspherical” elements near the diaphragm restore alignment of light rays at the image plane, maintaining high sharpness and contrast even at maximum aperture and can also be used at other points in the optical path to reduce distortion. Well-designed aspherical elements can reduce the total number of elements required in the lens, thus reducing overall size and weight. Advanced Aspherical (AA) elements are an evolved variant, featuring an extremely high thickness ratio between the center and periphery. AA elements are exceedingly difficult to produce, relying on the most advanced molding technology to consistently and precisely achieve the required shape and surface accuracy, resulting in significantly improved image accuracy and quality. Gyro sensors built into the lens detect even the slightest movement, and the stabilization lens is precisely shifted to counteract any image blur that might occur. The use of precision, quiet linear motors and technology inherited from high-end Sony professional camcorders results in exceptionally quiet, effective image stabilization that contributes to high-quality movies as well as stills. Only the middle groups of the optical system move to achieve focus, so the overall length of the lens does not change. Other important benefits include fast autofocusing and a short minimum focusing distance. It’s ideal for a wide variety of photos, including snapshots while strolling, night shots (thanks to the bright maximum aperture) and portraits with superb background/foreground blur.TechnologyCircular ApertureWhen changing your aperture to defocus the background, the light sources appear blurred. This ‘bokeh’ effect of the blurred background can be enhanced with circular aperture blades used in this lens. Conventional aperture blades have flat sides creating unappealing polygonal shaped defocussed points of light. α lenses overcome this problem through a unique design that keeps the aperture almost perfectly circular from its wide-open setting to when it is closed by 2 stops. Smoother, more natural defocusing can be obtained as a result.ED (Extra-low Dispersion) glassAs focal lengths get longer, lenses built with conventional optical glass have difficulties with chromatic aberration, and as a result images suffer from lower contrast, lower color quality, and lower resolution. ED glass dramatically reduces chromatic aberration at telephoto ranges, and provides superior contrast across the entire image, even at large aperture settings. Super ED glass provides enhanced compensation for chromatic aberration.Aspherical lens elementsAspherical lens design dramatically reduces spherical aberration while also reducing lens size and weight. Spherical aberration is a slight misalignment of the light rays projected on the image plane. This is caused by differences in refraction at different points on conventional spherical lenses which degrade image quality in large-aperture lenses. Specially shaped “aspherical” elements near the diaphragm restore alignment of light rays at the image plane, maintaining high sharpness and contrast even at maximum aperture and can also be used at other points in the optical path to reduce distortion. Well-designed aspherical elements can reduce the total number of elements required in the lens, thus reducing overall size and weight. Advanced Aspherical (AA) elements are an evolved variant, featuring an extremely high thickness ratio between the center and periphery. AA elements are exceedingly difficult to produce, relying on the most advanced molding technology to consistently and precisely achieve the required shape and surface accuracy, resulting in significantly improved image accuracy and quality.Lens-based optical image stabilizationGyro sensors built into the lens detect even the slightest movement, and the stabilization lens is precisely shifted to counteract any image blur that might occur. additional dog devices; sold separately). DOG LIST/GROUP MANAGEMENT Keep inactive dogs in your dog list, and manage active groups so you don’t have to add and remove dogs for every hunt. PUBLIC LAND BOUNDARIES Optional display of public land boundaries on topographical maps helps you know that you’re venturing where you’re supposed to be. TONE/VIBRATION Issue different levels of audible tone or vibration commands for quick adjustments to individual dogs. GARMIN EXPLORE APP Pair with the Garmin Explore app on your compatible smartphone to see real-time dog tracking information, save collections of dog tracks and replay tracks to see exactly what happened during your hunt. PRO VIEW COMPASS The pro view compass mode gives you simple, at-a-glance tracking that shows which direction and how far away your dogs are, plus you will see when a dog is “Treed” or “OnPoint.” MULTI-GNSS SUPPORT Access multiple global navigation satellite systems (GPS and Galileo) to track your pack with greater accuracy than GPS alone. TOPOACTIVE MAPS Our preloaded TopoActive mapping provides detailed views of terrain contours, topographic elevations, summits, parks, coastlines, rivers, lakes and geographical points. BIRDSEYE SATELLITE IMAGERY Download BirdsEye Satellite Imagery directly to the handheld for better-than-real-life views of your route, trailheads, clearings and more (active subscription required).

title: Hamile Smart Watch for Android Phones and iPhone Compatible, Smart Watches for Women Men 5ATM Waterproof Fitness Tracker with Heart Rate Sleep Monitor Step Counter Pedometer Stress Level, Lavender
description: Smart Watch for Android Phones & Smart Watch for iPhone Compatible Hamile Smartwatch with Heart Rate Monitor Pedometer Calorie Counter Compatible for Android Phones Samsung iOS Phone Hamile smartwatch is suitable for almost all smart phones, like Samsung, iPhone and so on. Compatibility: iOS 8.0 or Higher Version, Android OS 4.4 or Higher Version, BT 5.2 or Below Version. Strap Length: Fit wrist sizes from 5.5inch-10.25inch. Replaceable strap tips: strap width is 22mm, straps type is quick release spring bar. Enable to sync your data with Apple Health, Google fit and Strava. (go to VeryFit App-My-Setting-Data sharing and authorization) Display: 1.55 inch 360*320 Pixel TFT-LCD display, gives you a Larger Brighter Clearer view experience of your health data. Quick initialize Process: Paring the device with our app directly by scanning the Device’s QR code. Customize Watch Face: Being able to change your watch face everyday is surprisingly fun, on the weekends I can walk around with a cute carton on my wrist, but at the Monday morning office meeting I can wear a more professional watch face. Note: When you notice the new version of smart watch and VeryFit app, please update to the newest version for better using experience. More than 20 Functions Features with many practical tools, such as Stress Detection, Heart Rate Monitor, Sleep Records, Blood Oxygen Monitor, Call & Message Reminder, Pedometer, Calories, GPS Tracking, 5ATM Waterproof, Wrist Sense, Raise Wrist to Wake Screen, Customize Watch Face, Alarm Clocks, Stopwatch, Customize Timer, Breathing Activity Guide, Music Controller, Find your Phone, Drink Water Reminder, Sedentary Reminder, Weather and Temperature, Brightness Adjustment, Menstrual Cycle for Women, No Disturbing . And more great functions waiting for you to explore. 24/7 Heart Rate Monitoring The Smartwatch constantly samples your heart rate and will alert you if it stays too high or too low while you’re at rest. It also helps gauge how hard you work during activities. (Note: The smart watch isn't a medical device, not for medical purposes) Detects Your Blood Oxygen (SpO2) and Tracks Sleep Quality Using our smart watch, you can check how much oxygen is in your blood. (Please note: The data is only for Reference, Not for medical purposes) The fitness tracker tracks your sleep automatically, measuring deep, light and wake sleep. And wakes you up peacefully with a silent alarm. A Great Fitness Tracker Hamile running watch easily track your everyday activities, including pedometer measure your steps, distance traveled, and calories burned and more when you connect your fitness watch to our "VeryFit" app. Sleep Records We know that getting enough sleep is very important for everyone. Our phone watch can track and analyze your sleep time and quality, help you to improve your sleep and lifestyle. It shows deep sleep, light sleep, REM, awake and total sleep time. 14-Sports Tracking & Connected GPS Tracks up to 14 exercises like running, exercising, hiking, yoga and more. These exercise modes can help you better to track your workout, like steps, distance, calories, and make your daily work-out more effective. You can also activate GPS tracking on your phone and track routes you have traveled, then share the sports achievements data to social medial circle or your friends. Sedentary Reminders This android smart watch can remind you to walk or relax according to your setting times which help you to keep you in a good life habit. Music Control Once your watch is connected with your phone, you can directly play/pause music, skip songs or adjust volume on your watch without even taking your phone out of your pocket, letting you truly immerse yourself in the fascinating world of music or focus on your workouts. Weather Display Set the accurate location to get real-time display, view the current conditions for the day, along with tomorrow forecasts. It is very convenient for your daily or travel. Extra Smartwatch Band We designed 2 different wristbands for everyone especially. Wrist size from 5.5inch-10.25inch. The smart watches are suitable for teens, man, women and the elders. Read more Warm Notice 1.Please charge the smart watch to activate it at the first time when you receive it. 2.Please update the VeryFit app version and smartwatch version when there is new version.(How to check new version: VeryFit App>My>Check for Updates / VeryFit App>Device>Device Upgrade) 3.Can only reject the call. Can't make/answer phone call or send text messages. 4.It is 5ATM Waterproof. Can swim in swimming pool and sea, and daily waterproof. 5.We do not suggest you wear smartwatch when bathing, sauna, hot spring. Exceed 104°F water temperature will damage the smart watch. 6.Please keep BT on all the time, connection distance within 32.8ft/10m. 7.Regarding receiving message notifications, please follow the instruction carefully. 8.If the phone data is out of sync with the smartwatch data, please refresh Home screen on VeryFit. 9.The data of smart watch can not be used for medical data, reference only.

title: GM Genuine Parts 22753377 Radio Speaker
categories: Electronics,Car & Vehicle Electronics,Car Electronics,Car Audio,Speakers,Coaxial Speakers
description: Music will sound its best with ACDelco GM Original Equipment Car Speakers, and are GM-recommended replacements for your vehicle’s original components. Speakers turn electrical energy into mechanical energy to move air, using a permanent magnet and an electromagnet. The electromagnet is energized when the radio or amplifier (if equipped) delivers current to the voice coil on the speaker. The voice coil will form a north and south pole that will cause the voice coil and the speaker cone to move in relation to the permanent magnet. The current delivered to the car speaker is rapidly changing alternating current (A/C). This causes the speaker cone to move in two directions, producing sound. These original equipment car speakers have been manufactured to fit your GM vehicle, providing the same performance, durability, and service life you expect from General Motors.

description: Save the time and hassle of building Ethernet cables by using fixed-length UTP Cat6 Ethernet Network Cables from Monoprice! The ZERO boot series of Ethernet cables are designed for IT and data center professionals who prefer interconnect cables without the covers that protect the plug retaining clips, allowing for faster and easier cable connections. Monoprice Ethernet cables are made of 100% pure bare copper wire, as opposed to copper clad aluminum (CCA) wire, and are therefore fully compliant with UL Code 444 and National Electrical Code TIA-568-C.2 fire and safety standards, which require pure bare copper wire in communications cables.

title: Active Noise Cancelling Headphones,Wireless Noise Cancelling Headphone, Microphone 40 Hours Playtime Wireless Bluetooth Headphones 3D Low Bass Tone Fast Charge for Cellphone/Work/Gym/Travel
description: Enjoy a better wireless experience with Ulacici active noise cancelling headphones. The built-in Bluetooth 5.0 chip ensures easy connectivity to mobile devices within 33 feet (10m) for seamless audio/video sync. The wireless headset are compatible with all devices with 3.5mm plug cables and all Bluetooth-enabled devices such as iPhone, iPad, Android smartphones, MacBooks, TVs and more. With the built-in microphone, you can easily make hands-free calls or face-to-face meetings while working from home.       Active Noise Cancelling Headphones Ulacici Bluetooth headphones use a combination of active and passive noise cancellation, whether you're on a long flight or commuting to work, simply turn on the ANC button to enable noise cancellation, blocking out 90% of low frequency ambient noise, allowing you to focus more on what you want to hear. Comfortable Design Headphones lightweight structure, 90 degrees within the random rotation of the ear cups, adjust the headband, so you get the most comfortable wearing angle, long time to wear will not cause pressure on the ears. Portable Noise cancelling headphones can be folded and stretched, easy to carry, saving you a lot of space, is your best choice for travel, business, study, exercise.       USB-C Fast Charging Charging for 5 minutes provides 2 hours of listening, and a full charge supports 40 hours of playback time. Bluetooth Mode and Wired Mode When the cordless headphones run out of power, you can use the 3.5mm cable to enjoy a full day of music playback time without worrying about running out of power. Soft Earmuffs Headphones are equipped with the softest memory foam leather ear cups to ensure a comfortable and breathable fit.   High-Fidelity Sound Custom oversized 40mm dynamic drivers produce high-resolution sound, reproducing music with rich detail and stunning clarity for an immersive experience.
